dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Adams County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data group represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Adams County, Wisconsin in 2019 and includes the layers 'Adams_Roads_2019' and 'Adams_ROW_2019'. [Roads: Adams County Streets - Attribute table is formatted for use by the Spillman emergency dispatch system and the ESRI Alphanumeric geocoder. Metadata is minimal, only the attribute descriptions have been recorded. TG 20090910. ROW: Adams County ROW polygons.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: www.adamscountylandrecords.com
